                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "51cc0ef2-0e8c-4cfe-9c16-c3db34b0e501",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For today's lesson, we'll combine some of the information you've learned about mushrooms and bandages. We will spend our time together making Magical Bandages.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "721ec01f-46c1-4736-8891-b5f1577cfafc",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "To make a Magical Bandage, you will need two fresh, clean bandages. You then cover the bandages with a compound of Puffball and Fairy Parasol mushrooms with Yerba Buena from the Tower Garden.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "7c927b03-01f3-4e93-b153-00d277321ee7",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Take out your mortar and pestles and we'll get started with this, shall we?",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "920f7321-0773-41c5-945e-3ee286cb9df8",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "3ac1cad7-6c03-411f-8478-64f7596890e8",
                            "text": "Ask Something Sweet",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "e6a727e6-7dde-4905-acde-030948f9843b",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "37",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "53044cf1-4d6e-41d6-a785-305aed7f1152",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Will we be making enough Magical Bandages to restock the Infirmary? That sounds like a useful way to spend the afternoon.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "31de5d41-7bcf-45df-9f0f-5caa3d2ac954",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b9fcf37f-b835-4984-a883-03081177c8f1",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, you will be making some of the Magical Bandages for the Infirmary as well as for yourself, thank you.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "10793ef0-2d08-422b-9276-395503cdc880",
                            "text": "Ask Something Intelligent",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "363d7b86-6ccf-45fe-930b-9922e08c4196",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "37",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8a2f641a-ab70-4618-9813-c305208626f2",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "If you have to use up Puffballs, Faerie Parasols, and Bandages in order to make a Magical Bandage, is it worth it? Wouldn't it be better to just eat a couple of Puffballs for healing?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "d291cef8-63c8-4735-9d77-78876608dbf9",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b8479f68-06cc-402c-97f8-8b34d4532e9b",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "One advantage of using a Magical Bandage is that it won't make you feel sick when you try to heal with it. It's easy to apply a Magical Bandage to an open wound and it prevents the wound from getting dirty or infected.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "32ea5493-4368-46f1-aa74-343984090d42",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "If I'm in the middle of a combat and I get wounded, I'm much better off slapping on a bandage than trying to eat a mushroom and not get sick. So yes, a Magical Bandage is much better than raw mushrooms.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
